<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="N" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Narrow" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Narrow,</orth> 1) not broad, having but a small distance from side to side: <bibl n="shak. err 4.2.38" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. IV, 2, 38</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 2.8.28" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 8, 28</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 3.1.4" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 4</bibl>.* <bibl n="shak. aww 4.5.53" default="NO" valid="yes">All's IV, 5, 53</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 5.3.8" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 V, 3, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.2.63" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 2, 63</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.2.63" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 2, 63</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.2.201" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 2, 201</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.1.239" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C I, 1, 239</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 4.8.3" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 8, 3</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 3.3.154" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. III, 3, 154</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 2.4.88" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. II, 4, 88</bibl> <cit><quote>(from an inch n. to an ell broad).</quote> <bibl n="shak. jc 1.2.135" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. I, 2, 135</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. jc 2.4.33" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 4, 33</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 5.3.52" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 3, 52</bibl>.<lb />2) not wide, very limited: <cit><quote>'tis too n. for your mind,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.259" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. II, 2, 259</bibl></cit>; cf. <bibl n="shak. jc 1.2.135" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. I, 2, 135</bibl>. <cit><quote>most n. measure lent me,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 3.4.8" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. III, 4, 8</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>